              <span class="tooltiptext">Slender, cone-shaped with a sharp point<br><br>3/4 to 1 1/2 in long<br><br>1/4 to 1/2 of acorn is enclosed in a flat, scaled cap</span>
            </div><!--tooltip-->
          </div><!--outlineDrop-->
          <div class="leafOutline" id="drop6l" data-oak-type="Qwislizenii"><img src="images/leafOutline.png" alt="leaf outline" style="width:90%;">
            <div class="tooltip">-leaf-
              <span class="tooltiptext">Elliptical-shaped leaf with an abruptly pointed tip<br><br>1 – 1 1 /2 in long<br><br>Edges are usually spiny, but can be smooth<br><br>Glossy dark green</span>
            </div><!--tooltip-->
          </div><!--outlineDrop-->
