        <div class="treeName"><p class="oakName"><b>Leather Oak</b>   <i>(Quercus durata)</i></p></div><!--treeName-->
          <span class="treetooltiptext">Evergreen shrub<br><br>Grows to 10 ft tall and 8 – 12 ft wide<br><br>Can be bare and leggy up to 3 – 5 ft above the ground. <br><br>Dense, rounded growth</span>
        </div><!--treetooltip-->
 <div class="pictureHolder">
