              <span class="tooltiptext">Oblong, broad shape with sharp tip<br><br>1 to 3 in long<br><br>Acorn is held in a distinctive, heavy golden cap</span>
            </div><!--tooltip-->
          </div><!--outlineDrop-->
          <div class="leafOutline" id="drop9l" data-oak-type="Qchrysolepis"><img src="images/leafOutline.png" alt="leaf outline" style="width:90%;">
            <div class="tooltip">-leaf-
              <span class="tooltiptext">Leathery leaves with elliptical shape<br><br>Can have smooth or spiny edges<br><br>Shiny, dark green above, pale blue or gray below</span>
            </div><!--tooltip-->
          </div><!--outlineDrop-->
          <div class="barkOutline" id="drop9b" data-oak-type="Qchrysolepis"><img src="images/barkOutline.png" alt="bark outline" style="width:90%;">
            <div class="tooltip">-bark-
              <span class="tooltiptext">Bark is smooth and white when young, checked and gray with age</span>
